revworks 0.5 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.github.daytron.revworks
The main package.
com.github.daytron.revworks.authentication
Provides classes for user authentication, validation and login process.
com.github.daytron.revworks.component
Provides classes for custom or derived components.
com.github.daytron.revworks.data
Provides enumeration classes for static data of various information.
com.github.daytron.revworks.event
Provides classes for custom events and Guava's EventBus.
com.github.daytron.revworks.exception
Provides classes for custom derived exceptions.
com.github.daytron.revworks.model
Provides classes that represent tables in the database.
com.github.daytron.revworks.presenter
Provides classes for event handlers and column generators for Table object.
com.github.daytron.revworks.service
Provides classes for data services for insertions, updates and retrievals of data from the database for students and lecturers.
com.github.daytron.revworks.service.admin
Provides classes for data services for insertions, updates and retrievals of data from the database for administrators.
com.github.daytron.revworks.util
Provides classes for utility services such as notifications, String manipulations and PDF handling.
com.github.daytron.revworks.validator
Provides classes for user input login validation.
com.github.daytron.revworks.view
Provides classes for all views with GUI components.
com.github.daytron.revworks.view.admin
Provides classes for views used for administrators.
com.github.daytron.revworks.view.main
Provides classes for views used for both students and lecturers.
com.github.daytron.revworks.view.main.lecturer
Provides classes for views used for lecturers.
com.github.daytron.revworks.view.main.student
Provides classes for views used for students.
